        "subtitle": "Modern Damascus with Linen Micarta",
        "intro_content": "<p>The <strong>Hezhen B38L Elegant Series</strong> brings a modern aesthetic to Damascus knife design. Built with 67-layer Damascus steel and a 10Cr15CoMoV core at HRC 60, the Elegant delivers the same proven cutting performance as other premium Hezhen series. The difference is in the handle: linen Micarta — a layered composite material that is moisture-resistant, incredibly durable, and provides excellent grip even with wet hands. Where traditional wood handles demand occasional oiling and careful drying, Micarta handles are virtually maintenance-free. The Elegant Series is a Hezhen sub-brand offering, with the refined fit and finish that Hezhen is known for. For cooks who prefer a contemporary, professional look over traditional wood, the Elegant Series delivers Damascus performance with modern practicality.</p>",
